[br]Epic overwrites their snare (hint hint), also its more of a snare and doesnt last nearly as long. Whats this mean? It messes with their timing bad and it will unsnare much before the druid will be ready for it. My personal favorite tactic, pull a casting mob on the same faction as what he is quading, and boom, lots of fun. For best results use a wizard necro mage or enchanter, or, my personal favorite, all 4 plus a cleric. Fun fun fun fun.

